# Web & Admin — Next.js + TypeScript

## Stack
- Next.js (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- Cloudflare Pages deployment
- Axios with Bearer token interceptor

## Structure (web/)
```
src/
  app/          → Pages (App Router)
  lib/api/      → API client, generated types
  lib/auth/     → AuthContext, AuthProvider, ProtectedRoute
  components/   → Reusable UI components
  types/        → TypeScript types
```

## Admin Additions
- Sidebar layout with navigation
- Data tables with pagination
- Admin role guard (wraps ProtectedRoute)
- Stats/dashboard cards

## Patterns
- Server Components by default, `"use client"` only when needed
- Auth: OAuth redirect flow + optional password login
- Token stored in httpOnly cookie or localStorage
- API calls via typed Axios client
- Tailwind for styling, design tokens from `shared/design-tokens/`
- Error boundaries for graceful error handling

## Commands
- `npm run dev` or `task web:dev`
- `npm run build` or `task web:build`
- `npx wrangler pages deploy` or `task web:deploy`
